Name: Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen, Inc
Description: DELISTED - Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen, Inc. develops, operates, and franchises quick-service restaurants. The company operates in two segments, Franchise Operations and Company-Operated Restaurants. As of April 19, 2015, it operated and franchised 2,420 Popeyes Chicken & Biscuits and Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen restaurants in the United States, Puerto Rico, Guam, the Cayman Islands, and 27 countries internationally. The company was formerly known as AFC Enterprises, Inc. and changed its name to Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen, Inc. in January 2014. Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen, Inc. was founded in 1972 and is headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia.
